skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: know yourself
des: Know Yourself is a simple and quick personality test. With only five yes or no questions, it diagnoses your personality and returns your strongest personality trait. Knowing your strongest trait can help you build on it every day and shine even more!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
